user.biography: Food guy @mythical & @mythicalkitchen. #AHotDogIsASandwich Podcast. Did journalism once. Wrote a cookbook once. Got a lower back tattoo once. He/him.

node.text: Please make the hours of agony from the #OneChipChallenge @paquichips worth it by subscribing to the Mythical YouTube channel (link in bio). If you do not... well... nothing is gonna happen but I’ll be all like “aww man they didn’t subscribe to the Mythical YouTube channel, that sucks.” So, please. Do it. For me. Or do it for someone better than me if you have to. Thank you. I will continue to drink milk now.

node.title: I Ate the Spiciest Chip In The World. FOR YOU.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Josh Scherer on August 12, 2021 tagging @rhettmc, and @nicolehendizadeh. May be an image of 3 people, beard and people standing.

node.text: In case ya’ missed it, me and @nicolehendizadeh had the meat maven himself, @rhettmc, on A Hot Dog Is A Sandwich to talk about the greatest regional BBQ style and HIS ANSWER WILL SHOCK YOU!!! For real though, big thank you to Rhett and it was a great convo, you should listen to it. Link in the bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Josh Scherer on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: Hey good news! Me and @nicolehendizadeh are doing a meet and greet as well as a LIVE episode of our podcast at @vidcon this year! More good news— @burritoslapalma is like a 15 minute drive from the Anaheim convention center. Yeah, i’m already planning my meals. October 21-24, come down and hang out and please tell me in person how terrible my food opinions are! #VCUS21

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Josh Scherer on June 13, 2021 tagging @heritagebarbecue, and @khoibarbecue. May be an image of food.

node.text: Smoked pork shoulder bánh xèo. Brisket bánh mì. Sriracha molasses spare ribs. But the star for me here was the smoked bò lá lốt sausage link. Holy hell, haven’t had that dish in years and all that fragrant betel leaf inside the sausage just brought me right back to it. Collab from @heritagebarbecue in OC and @khoibarbecue from Houston. Blown away. Also I got to drink a bunch of beers starting at 9:30 am waiting in line so that’s always fun. Great food, great company, great Sunday. Can’t wait to run it back again soon.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Josh Scherer on May 25, 2021 tagging @nicolehendizadeh. May be an image of 2 people, biceps and people standing.

node.text: Is a hot dog a sandwich? I truly don’t know. That answer is between you and your god. What I do know is that a hotdog sandwich is a t-shirt, and you can buy it at Mythical dot com. I love this design so much. I remember talking about the illustration for the podcast like a year and a half ago, and @matthewedwyer knocked it out of the park. Also can’t say how proud I am of @nicolehendizadeh and the work that we put into the podcast, week after week. Like we had no reason to believe that A Hot Dog Is A Sandwich would be a success, and roughly 60 episodes later, here we are, slangin merch, loving every minute of it. Big thank you to everyone who’s been listening, supporting, and sending in your #opinioncasseroles! What a fun ride this has been, man. Much more to come as well, stay tuned 🙏🙏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Josh Scherer on April 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and pizza.

node.text: Sometimes, at the end of a long shoot day, you just gotta unwind and nap in a bed of pizza.... while your director stands over you and takes photos at a very uncomfortable angle because his grundle is in your direct line of sight. Anyways. Got a very very fun new video out with the whole squad @vianaiaustin @nicolehendizadeh @trevorevarts all about busting homemade pizza myths and you should watch it please! I love this series so much and am so proud of the work that we do. Is it perfect? Hell no! We’re fallible fudge-ups just like all of you. But I hope you have fun watching and i hope you can take something useful away from the series.

node.text: Birria de res soup dumplings—truly one of the most awesome foods to ever come out of @mythicalkitchen. Big thanks to @nicolehendizadeh and @trevorevarts and @vianaiaustin for doing a hell of a lot of recipe development on these. Big thanks to @luckyendings for editing the photos. Big thanks to @zack.rezowalli for giving me shit on slack. Big thanks to you if you watch the video on YouTube and if you don’t THANKS FOR NOTHING, YOU JERK!

node.text: I always assume that people know I have a lower back tattoo but after comments on today’s video where my shirt was riding up I realized at least some people do not know this fact! The even funner fact is that I got it because all of you fine people raised $30k for @nokidhungry, which is an awesome organization. That day reminded me of the awesome power the Mythical Beasts wield 🙏. You all rule so hard. Thank you for the continued support and I can’t wait to get more dumb tattoos for a good cause (as soon as it’s safe.) ((and I KNOW I still gotta get @bingingwithbabish’s face on my buttcheek))
